      <description>&lt;p&gt;Real estate has long been a cornerstone of wealth building, offering both passive income and long-term appreciation. In 2025, the landscape continues to evolve with new opportunities and challenges for investors.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Why Real Estate Investment Matters 
    &lt;div id=&#34;why-real-estate-investment-matters&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;
